sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin as EPMP Admin
    actor User as EPMP User 
    participant EPMP as EPMP <br/>Integration Service
    participant Vault as Secrets Manager/KMS
    participant IdP as Entra ID
    participant SFAuth as SuccessFactors <br/>OAuth Token Endpoint
    participant SFOD as SuccessFactors <br/>OData API
    participant SFSOAP as SuccessFactors <br/>CompoundEmployee API
    participant DB as EPMP User Tables
    participant CH as Cache 
    participant Audit as Audit<br/>/Sync Log

    Note over Admin,SFAuth: One-time client<br/>registration and key setup
    Admin->>EPMP: Configure<br/>SuccessFactors connection
    EPMP->>Vault: Store client ID,<br/>private key/<br/>certificate refs
    Note over EPMP,SFAuth: SuccessFactors OAuth client registration uses an X.509 certificate and returns an API key/client id

    Note over User,SFOD: Runtime <br/>on-demand lookup flow
    User->>EPMP: Open approved <br/>staffing screen
    EPMP->>Vault: Get client<br/>credentials/cert reference
    EPMP->>IdP: Request<br/>SAML assertion for technical user
    IdP-->>EPMP: Signed<br/>SAML assertion
    EPMP->>SFAuth: Request<br/> OAuth token (client_id + SAML assertion)
    SFAuth-->>EPMP: Access token
    EPMP->>SFOD: GET User / EmpJob<br/> / FO* entities with $select, $filter, $expand
    SFOD-->>EPMP: OData <br/>response Employee data
    EPMP->>DB: Insert/Update <br/>user data
    EPMP->>DB: Cache upsert<br/>reference data
    EPMP->>Audit: Log lookup<br/>and response status
    EPMP-->>User: Validated user<br/>/ data

    Note over EPMP,SFSOAP: Scheduled master-data sync/reconciliation
    EPMP->>Vault: Get SOAP API <br/>credentials / session config
    EPMP->>SFSOAP: Login
    SFSOAP-->>EPMP: Session cookie
    EPMP->>SFSOAP: query CompoundEmployee (full, snapshot, or delta)
    SFSOAP-->>EPMP: Hierarchical employee master data XML
    EPMP->>DB: Normalize and <br/>upsert employee/org/manager reference tables
    EPMP->>Audit: Record sync <br/>checkpoint and reconciliation status
    EPMP->>SFSOAP: Logout
    EPMS->>SF: CompoundEmployee delta sync
    SF-->>EPMS: Employee master data XML
    EPMS->>DB: Upsert master/reference tables